detour around earthquakedamaged interstate 880 in oakland calif 
i10 between lafayette and baton rouge la us 50 leading to 
maryland beaches stretches of interstate 75 in north monroe 
county mich i80 at parsippany nj and in clearfield and 
jefferson counties pa i5 from vancouver wash into portland 
ore and all routes into virginia beach va which police planned 
to close off due to violence sparked by college fraternity revelry 
last year 
