20yearold marketing major at the university of south carolina 
some have served in the unit for 18 years 
when i got out of the army i wanted to stay part of the 
military so i joined the guard william said 
until now that meant giving up a weekend every month two weeks 
each summer and occasional special duty like last years hurricane 
hugo 
but on sunday they lost their weekend warrior status when they 
were placed on alert for at least the next 90 days the guardsmen 
will be regular soldiers assigned to the us 2nd army 
