allusion to vladimir lenins pseudonym but the n signature was 
changed to z in the editing process 
malia wrote that he had decided to remain anonymous so he 
wouldnt compromise his friends in the soviet union and because 
the fall of the berlin wall and central european communism had 
not yet demonstrated that leninist regimes are mortal 
malia said the pseudonym was no longer necessary because 
communism has been defeated in the soviet union 
