arms and ammunition that is no longer the case 
brazil can build its own tanks and fighter planes and is eager 
to market them india builds large warships artillery and 
missiles countries from argentina to south korea china and south 
africa also have homegrown weapons capability 
in 197879 the united states and the soviet union conducted 
