has vehemently opposed intervention by the west african force 
about 3000 soldiers from ghana nigeria guinea sierra leone 
and gambia arrived in monrovia on aug 25 on troop transport ships 
under orders to end the eightmonth tribal war 
taylors fighters have attacked the force on several occasions 
the news agency quoted a 36yearold ghanaian teacher kwasi 
kwateng as saying rebels attacked a community of 2500 ghanaians 
in barnesville about three miles from monrovias port 
but it was not immediately clear how many caity of the 5000 people 
estimated to have died in the 
war have been civilians 
