control of monrovias major airfield and began to advance toward 
three beseiged embassies the capture of the spriggs payne airfield 
could allow flights of supplies and additional troops for the 
contingent said the sources who spoke on condition of anonymity 
soldiers at the airport today were trying to reach the ghana 
nigeria and guinea embassies on the citys outskirts in territory 
held by taylors men said sources in touch with the regional 
forces by radio 
taylor claims his forces hold several thousand citizens of 
countries participating in the military force 
what we are we doing right now is not unlike what other 
