the changes resulted in a 6 increase in the monthly mortgage 
payment to 700 
the july median income exceeded the 33579 needed to qualify 
for a medianpriced home a family earning that amount actually 
would qualify to buy a home priced at 100500 using conventional 
financing covering 80 percent of the cost 
