national rationing takes effect saturday 
in iraq and authorities have issued coupon books and set up 
centers to distribute food sources in baghdad said but the iraqi 
capital was already feeling the squeeze 
long lines snaked out of bakeries in baghdad residents said 
refugees fleeing iraq earlier this week reported long queues 
