on his arrival at lusaka airport 
in the past mandela has blamed buthelezi for the violence 
in other developments friday the government confirmed that 15 
prisoners would be released sometime after the weekend the 
government and the anc agreed aug 6 on a review process to free 
political detainees starting sept 1 
