arab foreign ministers ended a twoday 
emergency session friday with a new condemnation of iraqs invasion 
of kuwait and a call for iraq to immediately release foreign 
hostages conference sources said 
only 13 of the leagues 21 members attended the emergency 
meeting and only 10 of them were represented by foreign ministers 
