matter by secretary of state barbara roberts his democratic 
opponent in the governors race 
as im sure you will agree roberts wrote this mailing is 
an unconscionable attempt to exploit the vulnerability of people 
who cannot read fine print or who for some other reason may not 
succeed in deciphering the real purpose of the mailing and who 
will as a result suffer financial hardship 
frohnmayer concurred 
this fundraising gimmick by the national republican 
senatorial committee is a bad idea he told the associated press 
while our professional staff pursues the consumer protection 
aspect i will urge the national committee to pull it its bad 
public policy and its bad politics 
in washington dc gop committee spokeswoman wendy burnley 
