it won the academy award for best foreign film in 1985 and was 
rereleased 
several years ago last images of the shipwreck might have 
been considered a success because of the international prizes 
today it is viewed as a failure because of the box office 
argentinas movie industry is changing priorities and themes in 
part because it is on the verge of collapse state support has 
dried up movie fans watch more at home on video and cable tv and 
